  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 57-105-1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE PROGRAM THAT AUTHORIZES THE MISSISSIPPI DEVELOPMENT AUTHORITY TO ALLOCATE INCOME TAX CREDITS AND INSURANCE PREMIUM TAX CREDITS FOR TAXPAYERS HOLDING CERTAIN QUALIFIED EQUITY INVESTMENTS, TO TEMPORARILY AUTHORIZE ADDITIONAL INVESTMENTS FOR WHICH TAX CREDITS MAY BE ALLOCATED UNDER THE PROGRAM; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
